      <div class="text-sm text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">
        <div class="font-medium">Peak: Sat 2-4 PM</div>
        <div>Weekend preference</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="behavioral-analysis">Behavioral Analysis</h2>
  <p>
    Discover patterns in your shopping behavior that can help optimize your spending:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Impulse Purchase Detection</strong>: Identify unplanned purchases and their triggers</li>
    <li><strong>Brand Loyalty Analysis</strong>: Track your preference for specific brands over time</li>
    <li><strong>Seasonal Behavior</strong>: Understand how your shopping changes with seasons</li>
    <li><strong>Price Sensitivity</strong>: Analyze how price changes affect your purchasing decisions</li>
    <li><strong>Shopping Efficiency</strong>: Measure how well you stick to your lists</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="my-6 overflow-x-auto">
    <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
